  <summary date="2015-02-24T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">DHS Employee Retroactive Pay Fairness Act

This bill requires federal employees furloughed due to a lapse in appropriations when funding for the Department of Homeland Security expires under current law on February 27, 2015, to be compensated after the lapse in appropriations ends.</summary>
